creator: NextGen Socials Sports, INC.
descriptionHtml:
uSTADIUM is a sports app built exclusively for superfans that gives you access to all your favorite sports team's breaking news, rumors, blogs, content, and rewards you with points. It's the most engaging superfan experience on the sports web.

How it works: After selecting your favorite sports team on signup, you dive into a feed of content from other superfans like you. This content can be fast and short (like Twitter), or long and thought-out (like Reddit). You can create your own content where you can add pictures, videos, and even audios, and start engaging amongst your fellow superfans. You'll see a news ticker (similar to ESPN) and will sporadically get live sports news pushed to your device, depending on your preferences (similar to Bleacher Report).

The coolest thing about uSTADIUM is that we reward you ALL THE TIME with points through our gamification engine. You can even see where you stand vs other superfans in a live up-to-date leaderboard.

So say you create a post about New York Jets QB Sam Darnold that gets traction, you get points. Or you nail a tough NFL Super Bowl trivia question, more points. Or if Tom Brady was going to hit the under on 300.5 passing yards ... points, points, points!

The best thing about these points for superfans is that they can be used to get discounts on items like jerseys, apparel, subscriptions, experiences, etc from all our affiliate sports partners.

We'll soon launch a way for our top superfans on uSTADIUM (MEGAFANS) to MAKE MONEY!

Make sure you stay up-to-date on our all our releases and live breaking sports news by TURNING ON OUR NOTIFICATIONS!

We are changing the Sports Fan lifestyle, forever!

title: uSTADIUM: Sports News and Rewards for Superfans

creator: NextGen Socials Sports, INC.
descriptionHtml:
uSTADIUM is where fans break news, create content and make predictions that win you uSTADIUM points in the best sports app created. On uSTADIUM, you have real-time access to the latest scores, rumors, news, content, and fan hot takes.

Sports fans can finally build a name for themselves by breaking their own news and competing with their friends, family, and fellow fans through Takes, which are your predictions.

How Takes work is this:

1) Make a prediction ... "I think the Steelers win by 3 points and Najee has 100+ yards" or "Jalen Hurts has 25.5+ Fantasy Points"

2) Use your points based on how confident you feel ... 1,000 points.

3) Others agree or disagree by matching your points. A pot of points is set.

4) Whichever side wins splits the pot!

Once you have enough points, you can start redeeming rewards like t-shirts, gear, discounts from our store, partner rewards, etc.

uSTADIUM covers topics for all major American sports, including the NFL, NBA, MLB, NHL, PGA, and more. We also cover Fantasy Sports for Football, Basketball, Soccer, Hockey, and Golf.

There is no sports experience or community like uSTADIUM. Try us out today!
descriptionShort: Sports Platform that Rewards Top Fans With Points
